<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THANGTHAT NING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa dawtnak hi, A lian i a ngan ee
 Van in ngeih chunh fapa a kan pek
 Sualnak ngeilo mi Jesuh vailam cungah a thi.

[C1]
   Thangthat ning, Bawipa na min thiang cu
   Thangthat ning, Bawipa ka tuukhal ttha
   A dawtnak cu kei ca'h khuaruahhar
   Zungzal nunnak a ka pek i,
   Ka nunnak cu thiltha in a khahter ca'h
   Donglo thangthat ning Oh, Halleluijah.

[V2]
 Beidongh in ka um ah, ruahchannak na ka pek
 Harsat le zawtfah ka ton caan ah, ka theih piak
 Bawipa nih dawtnak tling he damnak a ka pek.</lyrics>
<key>B</key>
</song>